I&#39;m already so pleased with the research results I obtain that
anything better from box 31 will be extra whipped cream and cherries
on top of my enormous vat of ice cream. 

I am curious to see how the mini and Frank&#39;s compare. I feel that the
my minibox is a bit like a TARDIS in a way--I hate to say it has
bonded with me or imprinted on me (or I&#39;ve imprinted on it), but that
does seem to describe it. The entities operating through it have bent
their communication style to my circumstances. I will be curious to
see if 31 does something similar. Who knows? It may decide it likes my
son Nick over me, or my friend Julie.

Whatever happens, I shall enjoy the experience!

Ann

